The paper discusses a programming model for iterative computations that involves propagating changes (deltas) from iteration to iteration and efficiently updating state. This is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), and data science (cs.DS, cs.DL). The paper also mentions a runtime system (cs.SE) for executing and optimizing these programs.
